1
00:00:00,740 --> 00:00:05,080
You just admitted that
Oh Jang Mi ran her mouth.

2
00:00:05,740 --> 00:00:07,210
The mere fact...

3
00:00:08,080 --> 00:00:10,220
that Oh Jang Mi is at this company...

4
00:00:11,020 --> 00:00:13,990
proves that everything you've told me
was a lie.

5
00:00:15,520 --> 00:00:17,520
So stop playing me for a fool.

6
00:00:18,890 --> 00:00:21,090
Jun Ho, please, listen to me.

7
00:00:21,390 --> 00:00:23,030
Everything Oh Jang Mi is saying is a lie.

8
00:00:23,030 --> 00:00:24,330
You've got it all wrong.

9
00:00:24,630 --> 00:00:27,270
You can't believe a word she says.
It's all a misunderstanding.

10
00:00:27,570 --> 00:00:29,270
Please believe me. Please?

11
00:00:32,540 --> 00:00:33,840
Don't touch me.

12
00:00:35,570 --> 00:00:38,340
If I could,
I'd replace all the blood in my body.

13
00:00:39,710 --> 00:00:40,750
Mom?

14
00:00:41,310 --> 00:00:42,380
Don't make me laugh.

15
00:00:43,380 --> 00:00:45,750
Don't you dare use the word "Mom"
in front of me again.

16
00:00:47,450 --> 00:00:49,390
I want to erase myself from existence,

17
00:00:51,860 --> 00:00:53,390
having been born your son.

18
00:00:55,430 --> 00:00:57,000
I despise myself for being...

19
00:00:58,360 --> 00:00:59,700
born as your son.

20
00:01:03,570 --> 00:01:05,840
Jun Ho, my sweet boy!

21
00:01:10,880 --> 00:01:11,880
Jun Ho...

22
00:01:25,520 --> 00:01:26,520
Chae Hwa Young.

23
00:01:26,830 --> 00:01:29,660
It's not fair for you
to be heartbroken over just this.

24
00:01:30,530 --> 00:01:33,000
Compared to what
my family and I went through,

25
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:35,130
this is nothing.

26
00:01:35,970 --> 00:01:37,200
Stop feeling so sorry for yourself.

27
00:01:43,940 --> 00:01:46,140
(Director Ma Seo Rin)

28
00:01:47,110 --> 00:01:49,380
(Daehan Genomics Center)

29
00:02:07,030 --> 00:02:09,100
What's in that envelope?

30
00:02:09,530 --> 00:02:10,600
None of your business.

31
00:02:10,900 --> 00:02:13,840
Team Leader Jin, just do your job
and mind your own business.

32
00:02:18,810 --> 00:02:19,940
She's definitely up to something.

33
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:38,960
Seo Rin.

34
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:42,070
Why are you home at this hour?

35
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:47,470
I came to tell Grandfather something.
Is Grandfather in his study?

36
00:02:47,470 --> 00:02:50,010
He went to Dream.

37
00:02:50,010 --> 00:02:51,710
He said he has a board meeting.

38
00:02:51,910 --> 00:02:52,910
Really?

39
00:02:53,210 --> 00:02:56,450
If it's urgent, you can just tell me.

40
00:02:56,580 --> 00:02:57,680
No, that's okay.

41
00:02:57,680 --> 00:03:01,120
I'll go to Dream myself
and tell Grandfather in person.

42
00:03:14,430 --> 00:03:15,470
Hey, Hong Ju.

43
00:03:15,470 --> 00:03:18,140
Seo Rin stopped by,
saying she needs to see the Chairman.

44
00:03:18,340 --> 00:03:19,340
Really?

45
00:03:19,840 --> 00:03:22,810
Then what about the DNA test results?
Who were they for?

46
00:03:22,970 --> 00:03:25,080
Are you sure it was a DNA test result?

47
00:03:25,340 --> 00:03:27,950
I'm positive. I saw the envelope.

48
00:03:28,010 --> 00:03:32,080
Then do you think Seo Rin got a DNA test
with her mother?

49
00:03:32,980 --> 00:03:36,090
But why would she need
to see the Chairman?

50
00:03:36,220 --> 00:03:38,760
Mom, I have to go. I've got an idea.

51
00:03:39,690 --> 00:03:43,260
All that matters is that
we don't get caught in the middle, right?

52
00:03:43,700 --> 00:03:45,530
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

53
00:03:45,600 --> 00:03:49,630
That Oh Jang Mi revealed everything
to my Jun Ho!

54
00:03:50,540 --> 00:03:52,700
For Jun Ho to even know about the twin...

55
00:03:52,970 --> 00:03:57,140
means she told him she was Oh Jang Mi
and I was his birth mother.

56
00:03:57,310 --> 00:03:58,310
Wait, so then...

57
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:00,580
Oh Jang Mi knew all along that you were...

58
00:04:00,850 --> 00:04:03,550
- Jun Ho's birth mother?
- Yes.

59
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:08,220
When did that little witch
find out that secret?

60
00:04:08,650 --> 00:04:11,190
We'll be in huge trouble
if she tells Chairman Ma.

61
00:04:11,790 --> 00:04:13,520
We have to shut Oh Jang Mi up
before she does.

62
00:04:18,530 --> 00:04:20,670
- Ma'am.
- What is it?

63
00:04:21,370 --> 00:04:24,800
I'm here because you told me to keep
an eye on Director Ma.

64
00:04:25,500 --> 00:04:28,770
Director Ma had an envelope
that looked like DNA test results,

65
00:04:29,140 --> 00:04:30,640
and she left to go see the Chairman.

66
00:04:31,440 --> 00:04:32,940
- What?
- The Chairman is...

67
00:04:32,940 --> 00:04:34,980
at the company's headquarters right now
for a board meeting.

68
00:04:38,580 --> 00:04:40,490
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

69
00:04:44,890 --> 00:04:45,890
Team Leader Jin.

70
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:47,690
You're quite good at your job.

71
00:04:48,290 --> 00:04:49,460
Who else knows about this?

72
00:04:49,460 --> 00:04:51,160
Just my mother and me.

73
00:04:51,660 --> 00:04:53,600
We're on your team, ma'am.

74
00:04:53,930 --> 00:04:56,470
And we'll just follow your orders.

75
00:04:56,470 --> 00:04:57,570
That's good.

76
00:04:58,040 --> 00:05:00,370
Team Leader Jin,
you're sharper than you look.

77
00:05:00,870 --> 00:05:02,040
As for your mother,

78
00:05:03,340 --> 00:05:06,680
I'm going to reward her handsomely,

79
00:05:06,810 --> 00:05:08,950
so tell her to keep up the good work.

80
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:10,780
Yes, ma'am.

81
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:12,620
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

82
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,520
Is that cunning witch, Oh Jang Mi...

83
00:05:19,520 --> 00:05:21,490
really going to tell Chairman Ma
that Jun Ho and I...

84
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:23,390
are mother and son?

85
00:05:24,830 --> 00:05:26,700
Manager Lee has to hurry up and stop her.

86
00:05:27,370 --> 00:05:28,400
What am I going to do?

87
00:05:29,870 --> 00:05:33,940
(Chairman Ma Dae Chang)

88
00:05:42,780 --> 00:05:44,780
(Daehan Genomics Center)

89
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,560
Hello?

90
00:05:53,560 --> 00:05:56,260
Shin Ae Ran.
I've been waiting for your call.

91
00:05:57,560 --> 00:05:59,600
What? Where do you want me to go?

92
00:06:00,900 --> 00:06:02,030
Right. I know that place.

93
00:06:02,730 --> 00:06:03,970
Okay, I'm on my way.

94
00:06:14,150 --> 00:06:15,150
Hey, Baek Ho.

95
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:18,680
Hey, Jang Mi.
I finally heard from Shin Ae Ran.

96
00:06:18,820 --> 00:06:21,750
You heard from Shin Ae Ran? And?

97
00:06:22,850 --> 00:06:25,320
So you're meeting her there?

98
00:06:25,790 --> 00:06:27,390
Then I'm coming with you.
Let's meet her together.

99
00:06:27,860 --> 00:06:30,430
She must have been lying low,
spooked by Ssangkal's death.

100
00:06:30,630 --> 00:06:31,960
I'm surprised she managed to get in touch.

101
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:33,430
Jang Mi, where are you right now?

102
00:06:33,870 --> 00:06:37,000
I'm at Dream headquarters,
but I can head over right now.

103
00:06:37,100 --> 00:06:40,740
Actually,
we can't risk exposing Shin Ae Ran.

104
00:06:40,970 --> 00:06:44,880
I'll take her somewhere safe first,
and then I'll head to the office.

105
00:06:44,940 --> 00:06:45,980
I'll see you at the office.

106
00:06:46,440 --> 00:06:50,080
You might be right. If I come,
it could put her in more danger.

107
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:53,650
Okay, got it.
I'll see you at the office later.

108
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:54,920
Okay.

109
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:04,230
(Daehan Genomics Center)

110
00:07:29,120 --> 00:07:33,590
(Chairman's Office)

111
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,660
Chairman's office.

112
00:07:39,960 --> 00:07:41,700
Yes, understood.

113
00:07:46,500 --> 00:07:50,810
(Chairman's Office)

114
00:08:34,420 --> 00:08:37,120
(Daehan Genomics Center)

115
00:08:53,800 --> 00:08:54,810
Shin Ae Ran?

116
00:08:55,840 --> 00:08:57,140
I'm here now. Where are you?

117
00:09:02,710 --> 00:09:03,810
Okay, I see you.

118
00:09:09,790 --> 00:09:10,790
Hey!

119
00:09:15,190 --> 00:09:16,190
What do you think you're doing?

120
00:09:24,370 --> 00:09:25,500
You bastards!

121
00:09:55,630 --> 00:09:56,830
Look at this little punk...

122
00:10:05,740 --> 00:10:07,610
You should've watched your back.

123
00:10:08,980 --> 00:10:09,980
Let's go.

124
00:10:22,890 --> 00:10:24,900
Baek Ho? How'd it go?

125
00:10:24,900 --> 00:10:27,370
Hello?
Are you this patient's emergency contact?

126
00:10:30,000 --> 00:10:31,000
Patient?

127
00:10:31,540 --> 00:10:33,500
Is Baek Ho hurt?

128
00:10:33,740 --> 00:10:35,570
We're transporting him to
the Korea University ER.

129
00:10:36,010 --> 00:10:38,940
He's lost blood and needs surgery,
so please come to the hospital now.

130
00:10:39,210 --> 00:10:40,210
Hurry!

131
00:10:42,350 --> 00:10:43,550
Oh, no! Baek Ho!

132
00:10:47,520 --> 00:10:48,550
Was it you?

133
00:10:48,550 --> 00:10:50,290
Did you have Baek Ho hurt?

134
00:10:50,620 --> 00:10:53,220
This is the price you pay
for running that mouth of yours.

135
00:10:55,060 --> 00:10:56,130
This...

136
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:58,930
is something you will never show
to the Chairman.

137
00:11:02,230 --> 00:11:05,140
- Chae Hwa Young!
- You'd better be careful from now on.

138
00:11:05,670 --> 00:11:08,740
Especially when it comes to
running your mouth to the Chairman.

139
00:11:09,110 --> 00:11:10,710
If anything happens to Baek Ho,

140
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:12,980
I will destroy
your precious Kang Jun Ho...

141
00:11:13,380 --> 00:11:15,180
with my own two hands! Got it?

142
00:11:23,650 --> 00:11:24,660
Baek Ho!

143
00:11:25,220 --> 00:11:27,460
Stay with me! Baek Ho!

144
00:11:31,700 --> 00:11:32,700
Baek Ho!

145
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:34,100
What did you say?

146
00:11:34,830 --> 00:11:35,830
Baek Ho?

147
00:11:36,400 --> 00:11:39,400
Yes, all right, Director Ma.
I'm on my way.

148
00:11:40,070 --> 00:11:41,970
- What's wrong with Baek Ho?
- Was that Director Ma?

149
00:11:42,040 --> 00:11:43,410
They said Baek Ho's been hurt.

150
00:11:43,810 --> 00:11:46,210
I'm going to go see him first.
I'll call you after.

151
00:11:46,310 --> 00:11:50,080
Honey! What do you mean he's hurt?
How bad is it?

152
00:11:50,350 --> 00:11:51,380
I'll call you later!

153
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:53,750
But... Goodness.

154
00:11:54,020 --> 00:11:55,520
- Goodness.
- Careful...

155
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:57,660
(In Surgery)

156
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,560
Please, no.

157
00:12:05,460 --> 00:12:06,560
Baek Ho.

158
00:12:08,230 --> 00:12:09,530
Baek Ho, please.

159
00:12:09,870 --> 00:12:11,940
(Authorized personnel only)

160
00:12:13,670 --> 00:12:15,670
Baek Ho was attacked?

161
00:12:15,870 --> 00:12:17,840
I don't understand what's going on.

162
00:12:18,010 --> 00:12:19,040
(In Surgery)

163
00:12:19,040 --> 00:12:20,110
(Operating Room)

164
00:12:20,110 --> 00:12:21,250
(Authorized Personnel Only)

165
00:12:23,810 --> 00:12:26,820
Doctor, how is Baek Ho?

166
00:12:27,150 --> 00:12:29,820
The surgery went well, right?
He's going to be okay, right?

167
00:12:29,990 --> 00:12:31,990
Yes, the surgery was a success.

168
00:12:33,020 --> 00:12:34,020
Thank you.

169
00:12:34,490 --> 00:12:35,660
Thank you, Doctor.

170
00:12:35,660 --> 00:12:37,560
We'll have to monitor his progress.

171
00:12:38,300 --> 00:12:39,300
Okay.

172
00:12:43,730 --> 00:12:44,840
Baek Ho.

173
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:46,500
Thank goodness.

174
00:12:47,300 --> 00:12:48,640
What a relief.

175
00:12:53,710 --> 00:12:56,610
(CEO Chae Hwa Young)

176
00:12:56,980 --> 00:12:58,180
That brazen bitch.

177
00:12:58,850 --> 00:13:02,020
I shudder thinking about
how I agonized over Chairman Ma...

178
00:13:02,350 --> 00:13:03,490
finding out this secret.

179
00:13:04,590 --> 00:13:07,460
Fortunately, the meeting went long,
so she couldn't see Chairman Ma.

180
00:13:08,690 --> 00:13:10,290
But I'm worried about what she'll do now.

181
00:13:10,900 --> 00:13:12,200
What if she starts talking?

182
00:13:12,660 --> 00:13:14,330
She knows that Kang Baek Ho...

183
00:13:14,530 --> 00:13:16,630
and her family paid the price
for her big mouth.

184
00:13:17,330 --> 00:13:18,500
She must have learned her lesson.

185
00:13:19,870 --> 00:13:21,310
What happened to Ssangkal's girlfriend?

186
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,910
We lost her.

187
00:13:24,070 --> 00:13:26,980
But she saw what happened to Kang Baek Ho
with her own two eyes.

188
00:13:27,410 --> 00:13:28,880
She won't dare make a move for a while.

189
00:13:29,380 --> 00:13:33,020
We've taught a harsh lesson to
Ssangkal's girlfriend and Oh Jang Mi.

190
00:13:34,020 --> 00:13:36,090
They won't dare run their mouths
so carelessly now.

191
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:38,890
But if Jun Ho knows everything now,

192
00:13:39,690 --> 00:13:41,860
do you really think he'll still agree
to marry Oh Jang Mi?

193
00:13:43,260 --> 00:13:44,330
That's the problem.

194
00:13:44,760 --> 00:13:47,160
I have to make him marry Oh Jang Mi,

195
00:13:47,300 --> 00:13:48,930
but he found out everything about me.

196
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:51,640
Jun Ho is in love with Oh Jang Mi.

197
00:13:51,970 --> 00:13:53,370
Maybe even his possessiveness...

198
00:13:54,070 --> 00:13:55,810
is something he inherited from you.

199
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:58,880
The need to possess
whatever he desperately wants.

200
00:14:00,950 --> 00:14:01,950
That's right.

201
00:14:02,510 --> 00:14:03,810
He is my son, after all.

202
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:07,020
He wouldn't be my son
if he weren't ambitious.

203
00:14:07,590 --> 00:14:10,990
In any case, we should push
to move the wedding up.

204
00:14:11,720 --> 00:14:13,560
- And after that...
- After the marriage,

205
00:14:14,590 --> 00:14:16,290
I'll have to get rid of Oh Jang Mi.

206
00:14:30,640 --> 00:14:31,810
Listen well, Oh Jang Mi.

207
00:14:32,340 --> 00:14:36,510
I never needed two of you.
I only need one.

208
00:14:37,510 --> 00:14:40,780
I don't care if it's you,
and I don't care if it's Seo Rin.

209
00:14:41,190 --> 00:14:44,620
Actually, compared to you,
who's bent on revenge,

210
00:14:45,060 --> 00:14:47,830
maybe Seo Rin, lying there like a corpse,
is a better choice.

211
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:54,500
Stop crying.

212
00:14:55,170 --> 00:14:58,170
The surgery went well, and he's okay.

213
00:14:59,100 --> 00:15:00,440
Alright.

214
00:15:02,340 --> 00:15:05,340
The paramedics called you...

215
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:06,980
because Baek Ho had your number
on his screen.

216
00:15:07,950 --> 00:15:10,050
Thank you for coming at this hour,
Director Ma.

217
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:13,980
CEO Chae must be worried.
You should head back.

218
00:15:14,950 --> 00:15:16,090
Okay.

219
00:15:19,090 --> 00:15:21,160
My mother doesn't worry about me.

220
00:15:22,230 --> 00:15:25,860
She's probably with Manager Lee now.
She always is.

221
00:15:27,460 --> 00:15:30,000
You mean, even at this hour?

222
00:15:32,170 --> 00:15:33,900
They must be working late.

223
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:34,970
Working?

224
00:15:36,610 --> 00:15:39,780
Who knows if that's all they're doing?

225
00:15:41,010 --> 00:15:43,380
- What are you implying...
- Goodness.

226
00:15:44,050 --> 00:15:46,450
I seem to have spoken out of turn
about my mother's private life.

227
00:15:46,980 --> 00:15:48,150
Please just forget I said anything.

228
00:15:51,690 --> 00:15:52,720
But you know,

229
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:55,160
don't you find it strange?

230
00:15:56,590 --> 00:15:57,800
What do you mean?

231
00:15:58,260 --> 00:16:00,430
Your car accident, Professor Kang.

232
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:01,970
I just can't figure out...

233
00:16:01,970 --> 00:16:05,570
how the incident where my mother
was jailed for Oh Bok Gil's murder...

234
00:16:05,870 --> 00:16:10,410
and your car accident
ended up being connected.

235
00:16:11,610 --> 00:16:13,140
Manager Lee Kang Hyuk...

236
00:16:13,210 --> 00:16:15,680
has been handling all
of my mother's affairs like her shadow,

237
00:16:15,680 --> 00:16:17,080
taking care of everything for her.

238
00:16:17,310 --> 00:16:19,180
All the dirty work, too.

239
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:21,420
But...

240
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:24,720
why wasn't Manager Lee
involved in that accident?

241
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:27,490
I mean, my mother even went to jail.

242
00:16:31,600 --> 00:16:34,700
Oh my. Sorry, I'm just rambling.

243
00:16:35,130 --> 00:16:36,300
I should get going.

244
00:16:37,130 --> 00:16:38,270
Okay.

245
00:16:40,570 --> 00:16:41,670
Thank you, Director Ma.

246
00:16:47,910 --> 00:16:51,050
So Manager Lee wasn't involved.

247
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:53,480
Her mom's private life...

248
00:16:56,450 --> 00:16:58,290
Are Hwa Young and Manager Lee Kang Hyuk...

249
00:16:59,260 --> 00:17:00,320
involved like that?

250
00:17:01,460 --> 00:17:02,990
- Baek Ho... Honey...
- He's here.

251
00:17:03,330 --> 00:17:04,330
How is Baek Ho?

252
00:17:08,100 --> 00:17:09,170
Baek Ho.

253
00:17:09,830 --> 00:17:12,100
What on earth happened?

254
00:17:13,870 --> 00:17:16,770
Honey. What did they say about Baek Ho?

255
00:17:16,770 --> 00:17:17,940
Is he badly hurt?

256
00:17:18,780 --> 00:17:19,910
He'll be okay.

257
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:32,490
Seo Rin, I heard Baek Ho got hurt?
How is he?

258
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:34,120
The surgery was a success.

259
00:17:34,630 --> 00:17:35,760
He'll be fine once he wakes up.

260
00:17:35,990 --> 00:17:38,030
Did the doctor say for sure
that he'll be okay?

261
00:17:38,030 --> 00:17:39,830
Or is that what you want to believe?

262
00:17:39,830 --> 00:17:41,030
But Seo Rin,

263
00:17:41,430 --> 00:17:44,940
how did you find out Lawyer Kang was hurt
and went to the hospital?

264
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:48,340
I don't know. If you're so curious,
go ask him yourself tomorrow.

265
00:17:54,110 --> 00:17:56,680
Professor Kang, what brings you here
all of a sudden?

266
00:17:56,950 --> 00:17:58,480
Where is Manager Lee?

267
00:17:59,050 --> 00:18:00,150
Manager Lee? Why do you ask?

268
00:18:00,380 --> 00:18:02,620
What is your relationship
with Manager Lee?

269
00:18:02,990 --> 00:18:04,190
What do you mean, "what relationship?"

270
00:18:04,990 --> 00:18:06,560
He's my assistant.

271
00:18:07,090 --> 00:18:08,930
My executive assistant,
who handles all my affairs.

272
00:18:09,190 --> 00:18:10,890
Is that really all there is to it?

273
00:18:12,230 --> 00:18:15,230
When I listen to you, Hwa Young,

274
00:18:16,170 --> 00:18:18,700
I start to think
I've misunderstood things.

275
00:18:19,100 --> 00:18:21,870
But the moment I'm alone,
it just doesn't feel right.

276
00:18:22,610 --> 00:18:26,740
It's like I'm possessed.
I just can't make sense of anything.

277
00:18:28,080 --> 00:18:30,650
No, I mean...
I want to trust you, Hwa Young.

278
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:32,680
I'm only like this because
I want to trust you.

279
00:18:33,750 --> 00:18:34,750
Nam Bong.

280
00:18:37,790 --> 00:18:39,920
Nam Bong, you can be
such a child sometimes.

281
00:18:40,660 --> 00:18:42,560
Like a little boy throwing a tantrum.

282
00:18:43,830 --> 00:18:45,030
Hwa Young.

283
00:18:46,830 --> 00:18:48,670
You still don't believe that I love you?

284
00:18:49,930 --> 00:18:52,900
I heard you were marrying off
Jun Ho and Seo Rin.

285
00:18:53,300 --> 00:18:55,510
Hwa Young, you say you love me,
so how could you do that?

286
00:18:56,140 --> 00:18:58,810
- What's the problem?
- But that would make us in-laws.

287
00:18:58,880 --> 00:19:01,040
Is there some rule that says
in-laws can't be in love?

288
00:19:02,150 --> 00:19:03,150
Hwa Young...

289
00:19:04,010 --> 00:19:05,680
I had no choice.

290
00:19:06,180 --> 00:19:08,550
The Chairman adores Jun Ho...

291
00:19:08,550 --> 00:19:10,590
and is rushing
to marry him to his granddaughter.

292
00:19:10,820 --> 00:19:12,790
How could I possibly stop him?

293
00:19:13,390 --> 00:19:16,760
- But still...
- Nothing will change.

294
00:19:17,960 --> 00:19:20,000
It's not like our relationship
is out in the open.

295
00:19:20,730 --> 00:19:22,530
We've had to hide from everyone as it is.

296
00:19:22,830 --> 00:19:25,500
Do you really think their marriage
will change anything?

297
00:19:26,000 --> 00:19:27,200
No, but Hwa Young...

298
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:28,610
Enough.

299
00:19:30,610 --> 00:19:32,310
I don't want to think about
what happens later.

300
00:19:32,910 --> 00:19:35,150
Let's just follow our hearts
and stay like this.

301
00:19:35,710 --> 00:19:36,880
All right, Nam Bong?

302
00:19:41,320 --> 00:19:42,390
Let's go.

303
00:19:43,120 --> 00:19:44,290
We can talk outside.

304
00:19:45,660 --> 00:19:46,660
Okay.

305
00:20:00,770 --> 00:20:03,440
Manager Lee, can you drive my car for me?

306
00:20:05,110 --> 00:20:07,210
Hwa Young, you can drive yourself, right?

307
00:20:08,750 --> 00:20:11,320
Please let me borrow
Manager Lee just for today.

308
00:20:13,550 --> 00:20:15,920
Manager Lee, please take
Professor Kang home.

309
00:20:16,390 --> 00:20:18,520
- What about you, ma'am?
- I can drive myself.

310
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,160
All right then.

311
00:20:45,850 --> 00:20:46,850
Give me a break.

312
00:21:13,140 --> 00:21:14,850
We're here. You can get out.

313
00:21:15,350 --> 00:21:16,710
You're not even going to open my door?

314
00:21:16,850 --> 00:21:18,080
I thought your duties...

315
00:21:18,480 --> 00:21:20,320
were driver and assistant.

316
00:21:42,170 --> 00:21:43,970
What are you to Hwa Young?

317
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:47,310
And don't try to feed me that line about
being her secretary.

318
00:21:47,310 --> 00:21:48,350
I know everything.

319
00:21:49,380 --> 00:21:50,380
What?

320
00:21:51,420 --> 00:21:52,450
What is it you know?

321
00:21:54,580 --> 00:21:56,920
What exactly do you think you know?

322
00:21:57,320 --> 00:22:00,920
I know that you killed Oh Bok Gil
and framed me for it.

323
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:02,460
What are you talking about?

324
00:22:03,590 --> 00:22:06,400
- That's ridiculous.
- Is it?

325
00:22:06,660 --> 00:22:11,130
You were jealous of my relationship
with Hwa Young, so you framed me.

326
00:22:11,970 --> 00:22:13,700
Or were you two in on it together?

327
00:22:14,340 --> 00:22:15,870
What are you to Hwa Young?

328
00:22:15,870 --> 00:22:17,140
Shut your mouth, you punk!

329
00:22:19,440 --> 00:22:22,050
Do you have any idea
how patient I've been with you?

330
00:22:22,610 --> 00:22:25,680
I treated you with respect,
and it went straight to your head.

331
00:22:26,050 --> 00:22:27,050
Hey.

332
00:22:27,350 --> 00:22:30,450
You really think CEO Chae is in love
with a piece of trash like you?

333
00:22:31,120 --> 00:22:32,790
Snap out of it, you punk!

334
00:22:33,390 --> 00:22:34,590
You've got some nerve.

335
00:22:37,590 --> 00:22:38,730
I'm warning you.

336
00:22:39,430 --> 00:22:40,660
Watch yourself from now on.

337
00:22:41,200 --> 00:22:43,600
If you make a move on CEO Chae
one more time,

338
00:22:44,130 --> 00:22:46,440
you'll die at my hands,
and no one will ever know.

339
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:49,340
What? This is unbelievable.
Are you some kind of thug?

340
00:23:00,180 --> 00:23:01,220
Baek Ho.

341
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:04,760
Please open your eyes, okay?

342
00:23:06,220 --> 00:23:08,760
Open your eyes and look at Mom, okay?

343
00:23:11,390 --> 00:23:12,400
My son.

344
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:15,270
I...

345
00:23:15,600 --> 00:23:18,470
I may not have given birth to you,

346
00:23:20,170 --> 00:23:21,300
but there was never a time...

347
00:23:22,970 --> 00:23:25,010
that you weren't my son.

348
00:23:26,610 --> 00:23:27,740
The day I brought you home,

349
00:23:28,980 --> 00:23:30,180
your eyes were so...

350
00:23:31,750 --> 00:23:33,450
clear and bright.

351
00:23:36,820 --> 00:23:38,420
I truly...

352
00:23:40,560 --> 00:23:42,560
gave birth to you in my heart.

353
00:23:44,590 --> 00:23:48,830
You grew into such a good, kind man.

354
00:23:51,330 --> 00:23:53,270
I was always so grateful for that.

355
00:23:57,070 --> 00:23:58,070
Baek Ho.

356
00:24:00,840 --> 00:24:02,010
I love you.

357
00:24:03,080 --> 00:24:04,650
My son, Baek Ho.

358
00:24:09,690 --> 00:24:10,720
So please...

359
00:24:14,090 --> 00:24:16,530
Please, wake up.

360
00:24:38,550 --> 00:24:40,020
Even though the side dish shop
was trashed,

361
00:24:40,520 --> 00:24:42,590
at least your store is doing well,
so that's a relief.

362
00:24:43,150 --> 00:24:46,090
I can't believe that monster,
Chae Hwa Young, wrecked the shop.

363
00:24:46,220 --> 00:24:47,360
I'm so pissed.

364
00:24:47,660 --> 00:24:50,160
Why can't Jang Mi just go
and tell Chairman Ma everything?

365
00:24:50,360 --> 00:24:54,230
I think she's afraid to tell him the truth
in case he collapses from the shock.

366
00:24:54,300 --> 00:24:56,130
Suk Hee likes meat.

367
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:58,400
Jang Mi likes sweet rice punch.

368
00:24:58,470 --> 00:24:59,870
Let's give her sweet rice punch,
Tae Pyung.

369
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:03,540
Okay, Mom.
I'll see if I can give Jang Mi a call.

370
00:25:09,150 --> 00:25:12,350
- Jang Mi. I was about to call you...
- Tae Pyung.

371
00:25:12,780 --> 00:25:14,950
Baek Ho got hurt.

372
00:25:15,220 --> 00:25:17,650
What? Baek Ho's hurt?

373
00:25:18,220 --> 00:25:20,120
Is it serious? Where are you now?

374
00:25:26,000 --> 00:25:27,000
Jun Ho.

375
00:25:27,730 --> 00:25:30,030
Good timing. I was just getting home
when you called.

376
00:25:30,230 --> 00:25:33,400
If I went in, I'd have gotten an earful
about going out again.

377
00:25:33,570 --> 00:25:34,970
Is that really what's important right now?

378
00:25:36,140 --> 00:25:37,410
Then what is?

379
00:25:37,470 --> 00:25:40,780
You hurt Baek Ho, didn't you?

380
00:25:41,880 --> 00:25:43,010
What are you talking about?

381
00:25:43,380 --> 00:25:44,380
Don't play dumb.

382
00:25:44,880 --> 00:25:47,120
Because Oh Jang Mi said
she wanted to marry Baek Ho,

383
00:25:47,580 --> 00:25:49,650
you decided you had to get rid of him?

384
00:25:50,050 --> 00:25:52,460
- Jun Ho.
- Your excuses won't work on me.

385
00:25:53,590 --> 00:25:56,730
The fact alone that
Director Ma was Oh Jang Mi...

386
00:25:57,560 --> 00:25:59,700
tells me everything
I need to know about you.

387
00:26:00,830 --> 00:26:02,300
You've got it all wrong, Jun Ho.

388
00:26:02,570 --> 00:26:04,970
Are you trying to ruin
my brother now, too?

389
00:26:06,000 --> 00:26:07,940
We may not be blood-related,

390
00:26:08,870 --> 00:26:10,740
but we've lived together for 30 years.

391
00:26:11,910 --> 00:26:14,110
Our bond is much stronger
than any I have with you.

392
00:26:14,950 --> 00:26:16,380
Wasn't ruining my father enough?

393
00:26:16,910 --> 00:26:18,320
Now you're going after my brother, too?

394
00:26:18,620 --> 00:26:21,180
- Jun Ho, that's not what happened.
- And after all that,

395
00:26:22,290 --> 00:26:24,250
you still expect me
to want to be your son?

396
00:26:25,290 --> 00:26:27,660
You still want to keep
pretending you're my mother?

397
00:26:29,730 --> 00:26:30,860
Don't even dream of it.

398
00:26:33,160 --> 00:26:34,200
Jun Ho.

399
00:26:35,630 --> 00:26:36,800
Forget about everything else.

400
00:26:37,270 --> 00:26:40,840
Just focus on taking over Dream Group.
Only that. Okay?

401
00:27:52,280 --> 00:27:53,280
Baek Ho.

402
00:27:54,880 --> 00:27:55,880
I'm so sorry.

403
00:27:58,580 --> 00:27:59,650
This decision...

404
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:02,520
is what's best for everyone.

405
00:28:32,620 --> 00:28:34,080
(The First Man)

406
00:28:34,220 --> 00:28:36,020
I'll marry Kang Jun Ho.

407
00:28:36,290 --> 00:28:37,450
But on one condition.

408
00:28:37,590 --> 00:28:39,620
Don't touch Baek Ho, the man I love.

409
00:28:40,360 --> 00:28:43,060
You're Oh Jang Mi, right?

410
00:28:43,190 --> 00:28:44,960
And you're saying you'll marry me?

411
00:28:45,460 --> 00:28:48,470
Whether this marriage happens or not
is up to you, Jun Ho.

412
00:28:48,870 --> 00:28:52,300
Chae Hwa Young, you're a piece of filth
worse than garbage.

413
00:28:52,700 --> 00:28:53,740
What was that?

414
00:28:53,870 --> 00:28:55,270
What do you think you're doing?

415
00:28:55,870 --> 00:28:57,570
I see you've become quite the vixen.

416
00:29:00,640 --> 00:29:02,650
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
